title: Disney’s Weird Censorship, Rats Inherit New York 4.16.20
itunes:title: Disney’s Weird Censorship, Rats Inherit New York 4.16.20
description:
In episode 610, Jack, Miles, and Jamie are joined by comedian, Get Rich Nick, and Deckheads podcast host Nick Turner to discuss an ER doctors experience in New York, Kellyanne Conway's lack of facts, Democrats trying to push a bill to give Americans 2k a month, LA coronavirus deaths going up

FOOTNOTES:

  1. I’m an E.R. Doctor in New York. None of Us Will Ever Be the Same.
  2. Kellyanne Attacks WHO’s Command of ‘Facts and Figures’ With Nonsensical ‘COVID-1’ Dig
  3. Coronavirus Relief: Proposed Bill Would Give Americans $2,000 A Month During Pandemic
  4. L.A. County confirms 40 new coronavirus deaths, the highest toll in a single day
  5. Rat Expert Predicts Rat Turf Wars As Some Parts Of NYC Produce Less Trash
  6. 5 Reasons Rats Are Way Scarier Than You Think
  7. Disney Plus racks up 50m subscribers in five months
  8. Disney Plus’ butt cover-up hides a much bigger problem
  9. On Disney+, Not All Butts Are Created Equal
  10. Disney+ users baffled by Lilo and Stitch alteration: ‘It’s annoying how they’ve changed scenes’
  11. Filtering Your World Is Understandable—But It's Not Helpful
  12. WATCH: Cougar - Rhinelander
